Introducing the Breville Smart Fryer. The first deep fryer that adjusts time and temperature to suit what you're cooking. Let's see it in action.  From fries to fish and wings to donuts, this versatile fryer ensures your food is always crisp. The Smart Fryer, brought to you by the food thinkers of Breville
